Export the jar from here:
https://github.com/uriel-frankel/android-code-coverage/raw/master/hellojacoco/android-jacoco-the-missing.jar

Execute the jar using the following command:

java -jar android-jacoco-the-missing.jar -f /path/to/coverage.ec -p ./<project-package-name>

Make sure to create a folder with <project-package-name> and keep all code coverage files inside this folder. The project directory (<project-package-name>) should contain the 
non-instrumented class files inside <project-package-name>/app/build/intermediates/classes

This will generate a folder named coveragereport/ one level above project's folder.
